	<h1><strong>Brief BioData</strong></h1>
	<h2><strong>Curriculam Vitae of Gajendra P.S. Raghava</strong></h2>
	
<p>(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Name in full:&nbsp;</strong>Raghava, Gajendra Pal Singh&nbsp;</p>
<p>(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Nationality:&nbsp;</strong>Indian</p>
<p>(3)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Field of Specialization:&nbsp;</strong>Bioinformatics</p>
<p>(5)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Designation:&nbsp;</strong>Professor</p>
<p>(6)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Official Address:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Indraprastha Institute of Information Technology, Okhla Phase III, New Delhi<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Tel:&nbsp;</strong>011-26907444 &nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>E-mail:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:raghavagps@gmail.com">raghavagps@gmail.com</a></p>
<p>(7)&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Academic career and professional attainments:&nbsp;</strong><br>
&nbsp;</p>

